    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >集结！星际猎人的狂欢派对</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在银河系最黑暗的角落，“猎人天堂”公会正在招募精英。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《赏金乱斗：头号通缉》是一款<strong>快节奏俯视角动作射击游戏</strong>。在这里，所谓的正义不过是价高者的筹码。作为一名星际赏金猎人，你可单人探索或与好友组队，深入充满敌意的星球，追捕那些全宇宙最危险的罪犯。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097510/extras/f8830cfa8f82630d314d33e6ef72aef7.poster.avif?t=1770957990\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097510/extras/f8830cfa8f82630d314d33e6ef72aef7.webm?t=1770957990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097510/extras/f8830cfa8f82630d314d33e6ef72aef7.mp4?t=1770957990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >独创“拉索”机制</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>机动为王：</strong> 利用拉索跨越地形深渊，瞬间切入切出战场，或是在战斗中操作特殊机关。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>处决快感：</strong> 寻找最佳时机，对失衡的敌人发动致命处决，打出成吨伤害！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>把控全场：</strong> 灵活运用拉索，拯救队友，极限输出，秀翻全场！</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097510/extras/b88e475db4f96d6257f60392fe404b2e.poster.avif?t=1770957990\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097510/extras/b88e475db4f96d6257f60392fe404b2e.webm?t=1770957990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097510/extras/b88e475db4f96d6257f60392fe404b2e.mp4?t=1770957990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >你的猎人，独一无二</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >首发8位性格迥异的赏金猎人，拒绝“换皮”体验！每一位猎人都拥有完全独立的<strong>攻击模组、战斗机制和战术定位</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过黑市商人购买违禁装备，自由搭配你的战斗流派，每次出击都是全新体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097510/extras/3cc3ddfd67ba5d6fc7d6216d31524e91.poster.avif?t=1770957990\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097510/extras/3cc3ddfd67ba5d6fc7d6216d31524e91.webm?t=1770957990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097510/extras/3cc3ddfd67ba5d6fc7d6216d31524e91.mp4?t=1770957990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >合作缉凶……然后背刺？！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏支持<strong>1-4人在线/本地联机</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在大部分时间里，你们是生死与共的战友，需要默契配合，共同在随机生成的关卡中完成悬赏任务，击败压迫感十足的星球BOSS。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但在BOSS倒下的那一刻，友谊的小船可能就要翻了……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>“最终对决”机制：</strong> 赏金只有一份，荣耀只归一人。在撤离前的最后时刻，用尽浑身解数击败你的“队友”，抢夺头号猎人的宝座！哪怕是几秒钟的内斗，也能让你笑得停不下来。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097510/extras/a2764a69c2eba441eb8baca8326e31c6.poster.avif?t=1770957990\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097510/extras/a2764a69c2eba441eb8baca8326e31c6.webm?t=1770957990\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3097510/extras/a2764a69c2eba441eb8baca8326e31c6.mp4?t=1770957990\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>极速动作体验：</strong> 肾上腺素飙升的快节奏战斗，无尿点，就是干！</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>星际赛博风情：</strong> 融合了像素艺术与赛博朋克的独特视觉风格，探索那些混乱又迷人的法外之地。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>局局有新意：</strong> 随机生成的房间、多变的敌人配置与可选的挑战任务，让你的每一次狩猎之旅都充满未知。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>欢乐开黑首选：</strong> 无论是通力合作还是互相伤害，这都是一款不仅考验操作，更考验“友情”的派对神器。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好成为银河系最“声名狼藉”的传说了吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
